data.title: Chauncey Billups, Basketball Player
data.meta_description: Chauncey Billups stats and bio. Stats averages season by season. Quick access to game by game stats.
data.text:
Chauncey Billups - Points

Chauncey Billups scores a career high 39 points (2010)

On February 05, 2010, Chauncey Billups set his career high in points in a NBA game. That day he scored 39 points in Denver's road win against LA Lakers, 113-126. He also had 4 rebounds, 8 assists, 1 steal. He shot 3/7 from two, 9/13 from three, shooting at 60.0% from the field. He also shot 6/8 from the free-throw line.

Chauncey Billups - Rebounds

Chauncey Billups grabs a career high 12 rebounds (2006)

On December 29, 2006, Chauncey Billups set his career high in rebounds in a NBA game. That day he grabbed 12 rebounds in Detroit's home loss against Indiana, 92-93. He also had 23 points, 5 assists, 1 steal and 1 block.

Chauncey Billups - Assists

Chauncey Billups gives a career high 19 assists (2005)

On December 14, 2005, Chauncey Billups set his career high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 19 assists in Detroit's home win against Sacramento, 109-98. He also had 28 points, 3 rebounds, 1 steal.

Chauncey Billups - Steals

Chauncey Billups has a career high 7 steals (1998)

On January 23, 1998, Chauncey Billups set his career high in steals in a NBA game. That day he reached 7 steals in Boston's road win against Atlanta, 85-89. He also had 18 points, 5 rebounds and 8 assists.

Chauncey Billups - Blocks

Chauncey Billups blocks a career high 3 shots (2002)

On February 15, 2002, Chauncey Billups set his career high in blocks in a NBA game. That day he went for 3 blocks in Minnesota's home loss against Denver, 98-99. He also had 10 points, 6 rebounds and 5 assists.

Chauncey Billups - Efficiency

Chauncey Billups records a career high 45 efficiency rating (2010)

On February 25, 2010, Chauncey Billups set his career high in efficiency in a NBA game. That day he accomplished 45 efficiency in Denver's road win against Golden State, 112-127. He also had 37 points, 6 rebounds and 9 assists.
